  "instructions": [
    "Thread the chicken, red bell pepper, zucchini, and onion onto metal skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lemon zest, lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the skewers with the lemon mixture.",
    "Heat an iron teppan or grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cook the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "While the skewers cook, melt the tempering chocolate in a small saucepan over low heat.",
    "Once the skewers are cooked, brush them with the melted chocolate.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve immediately."
  ],
